h3. Problem
Data in {{sequence_value_item}} table is not consistent with other tables, for examples
{code:borderStyle=solid}
SQL> select * from sequence_value_item where seq_name = 'OptionConfiguration';
SEQ_NAME                                                         SEQ_ID
------------------------------------------------------------ ----------
OptionConfiguration                                              861700

SQL> select max(id) from optionconfiguration;
   MAX(ID)
----------
    861886
{code}
MaxID: *861886* > SEQ_NAME_OptionConfiguration: *861700* which is the problem. 

h3. Suggested Solution
It will be really useful to include an integrity check on the id value within the table {{sequence_value_item}} and all related tables needs it to provide the next ID. It will give the administrator the indication potential issue and fix it with a maintenance window.

